WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.680
I've heard that Bay High Park is very beautiful.

00:03.680 --> 00:07.320
Yes, it is. Shall we go for a walk there?

00:07.320 --> 00:09.520
That's a great idea.

00:09.520 --> 00:12.880
Maybe Darming and Betty will come too.

00:12.880 --> 00:16.120
Let's tell them that we're going to spend the day there.

00:16.120 --> 00:18.920
I guess it's a very popular place.

00:18.920 --> 00:20.960
Will there be lots of people there?

00:20.960 --> 00:24.960
Well, lots of people go there, but it's a big park,

00:24.960 --> 00:27.160
so I don't think it'll be very busy.

00:27.160 --> 00:28.640
I hope not.

